sql: SELECT COURSEalias0.DEPARTMENT , COURSEalias0.NAME , COURSEalias0.NUMBER FROM COURSE AS COURSEalias0 , PROGRAM AS PROGRAMalias0 , PROGRAM_COURSE AS PROGRAM_COURSEalias0 WHERE PROGRAM_COURSEalias0.CATEGORY = "MDE" AND PROGRAM_COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID = COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID AND PROGRAMalias0.NAME = "CS - LSA" AND PROGRAMalias0.PROGRAM_ID = PROGRAM_COURSEalias0.PROGRAM_ID ;
